Package it.polimi.ingsw.Network.Server

Class TCPConnect

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.Network.Server.TCPConnect
All Implemented Interfaces:
Connection
public class TCPConnect extends Object implements Connection
Represents a TCP connection implementation of the Connection interface. It maintains a socket connection with the server and provides methods to send and receive messages.
